==Finishing up==
===Talking to Curator Haig Halen===
* '''Curator Haig Halen:''' Welcome to the museum of Varrock.
* '''Player:''' I have half the shield of Arrav here. Can I get a reward?
* '''Curator Haig Halen:''' The Shield of Arrav! Goodness, the Museum has been searching for that for years! The late King Roald II offered a reward for it years ago!
* '''Player:''' Well, I'm here to claim it.
* '''Curator Haig Halen:''' Let me have a look at it first.
** {{tbox|pic=Broken shield (left) detail.png|The curator peers at the shield.}}
* '''Curator Haig Halen:''' This is incredible!
* '''Curator Haig Halen:''' That shield has been missing for over twenty-five years!
* '''Curator Haig Halen:''' Leave the shield here with me and I'll write you out a certificate saying that you have returned the shield, so that you can claim your reward from the King.
* '''Player:''' Can I have two certificates please?
* '''Curator Haig Halen:''' Yes, certainly. Please hand over the shield.
** {{tbox|pic=Broken shield (left) detail.png|You hand over the shield half.}}
** {{tbox|pic=Half certificate (left) detail.png|The curator writes out two half-certificates.}}
